self = <binarySearchTree3.DoubleLinkedList object at 0x7fd900a86c20>, val = None

    def remove(self, val):
        """Remove first occurance of val from list."""
        curr = self.head
        while curr:
            if curr.data is val:
                if self._length == 1:

                self._length -= 1
                return

    def delete(self, val):
        """Remove a node from the tree."""
        if self._size < 1 or not self.contains(val):
            return
    
        node = self.search(val)
    
        if not node._is_leaf():  # no children
            if node.parent:
                setattr(node.parent, node._side(), None)
            else:
                self.root = None
    
        elif node._is_interior():  # two children
            next_node = self._find_replacement(node)
            self._size += 1
            self.delete(next_node.val)
            node.val = next_node.val
    
        else:  # one children
